在消费者受威胁后由民警护送其返店的情况。 相关问题 1 月初在三亚的海鲜市场买了几个活的海胆，结果打开一看西米都木有 老板说海南海胆就这样，求解！？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d064e37e660d6b1cef2e06f1c4e67d0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "539 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454031777"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iusuyx/DK7YNtEAMaCDYzMTc1NTE3IPGCyoMGMAQ4owNACnIJNDU0MDMxNzc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1618143231.5944743", "card_id": "Q_453333735", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 92}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价天蚕土豆新书《万相之王》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "436 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453333735"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iusuyx/DK7YNtEAMaCDYzMDIwNDAzIPzNtIMGMAw4zAFAC3IJNDUzMzMzNzM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1618143231.5947542", "card_id": "Q_348287427", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 228}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "爸爸去世继承的房产，现在要出售，房屋中介说百分之二十的遗产税，是这样吗？100 万房子 20 万的税？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e273021517c0a15b6f234938a73e68df_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "434 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/348287427"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iusuyx/DK7YNtEAMaCDM5Njc1MjU5IO3dvewFMBk4shZADHIJMzQ4Mjg3NDI3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1618143231.5951457", "card_id": "Q_422300296", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 148}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "假如胡万冤枉张牧之吃两碗凉粉，牧之会怎么处理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e914367